! Note: This Goggle is designed to enhance the browsing experience for those looking to purchase items directly from other individuals. It prioritizes peer-to-peer marketplaces, local classifieds, and community-based selling platforms while slightly downranking traditional retail stores. This provides users with easier access to secondhand goods, unique items, and local sellers.
